e guaranteed by the affordable care act . # protectourcare https : //t.co/mkfdtukgl5 there ’ s someone out there who only you can get through to this election . they won ’ t listen to political ads , but they will listen to you . you have the power to help them vote . join @ women4biden 's gotv marathon — and catch me there tomorrow at 3pm et ! ➡️ https : //t.co/mkulys7sre https : //t.co/dyjmsul1v7 here for this by @ thekelleyshow in @ theybf ! ! we know @ joebiden and @ kamalaharris will make sure sexual and reproductive health , and the intersectional issues patients face , don ’ t take the back seat . so we 've got to vote ! # wedecide2020 https : //t.co/rstg6bwain
