rt @ ajentleson cbs poll showing biden winning 50-31 was of undecided voters . cnn poll showing a tie was of 'debate watchers . ' # debatehealth the verdict rt @ sarah_boxer : cbs news snap poll of uncommitted voters : 50 % biden won ; 31 % ryan ; 19 % tie https : //t.co/ienmtypj # debatehealth @ premieradvisor @ wsj @ joebiden thanks for the kind words . more to come . hope you stay safe and well . @ facethenation @ margbrennan @ joebiden @ surgeon_general @ jeromeadamsmd recruitment of minorities has been challenging because of longstanding distrust , bias in the medical system and structural barriers that reduce access to care . we must redouble our efforts to build trust , partnership , and participation in trials . ( end ) @ facethenation @ margbrennan @ joebiden @ surgeon_general @ jeromeadamsmd @ cdcgov loneliness has serious consequences for our physical and mental health , increasing our risk of depression and anxiety among other conditions . the cancellation of school and reduced social contact has placed a strain on the social health of millions of children and adults . ( 1/x ) @ facethenation @ margbrennan @ joebiden @ surgeon_general @ jeromeadamsmd it is essential the clinical trials recruit patients of diverse racial/ethnic backgrounds and ages . if they fail to do so , we will be less confident that the results of the vaccine trials apply to everyone . ( 1/x ) @ facethenation @ margbrennan @ joebiden he will need to communicate regularly and transparently with the public and allow scientific experts to speak directly to the media . ( 3/x ) @ facethenation @ margbrennan @ joebiden @ surgeon_general @ jeromeadamsmd @ cdcgov we can and must do better in terms of our national response to # covid19 - but we can also use this pandemic to take stock of our lives , to remember it is our relationships that bring us our greatest joy , and to recommit to the people in our lives . ( 4/x ) @ facethenation @ margbrennan @ joebiden it will mean putting in place the strategy and resources necessary to reopen schools and workplaces . it will mean choosing the right people to lead his covid19 response team . ( 2/x ) @ facethenation @ margbrennan @ joebiden @ surgeon_general @ jeromeadamsmd @ cdcgov 3 simple ways to strengthen connection during the # covid19 pandemic : 1 ) spend 15 minutes each day talking to someone you care about . a little time goes a long way to creating connection . ( 5/x ) @ facethenation @ margbrennan @ joebiden if @ joebiden serves as president , he will need to rebuild public trust in the # covid19 response right away . that will mean laying out a detailed plan for expanding testing , building contact tracing capacity , and distributing a vaccine ( he 's already started ) ( 1/x ) @ facethenation @ margbrennan @ joebiden @ surgeon_general @ jeromeadamsmd @ cdcgov this is one of many reasons it is so urgent that we get # covid19 cases down in communities so kids can more safely get back to school . ( 2/x ) thank you @ joebiden for recognizing the challenge of loneliness and the power of human connection - especially during # covid19 . also , thank you for making my mother famous 😊 stay safe and well , sir . https : //t.co/qrefosjaij @ facethenation @ margbrennan @ joebiden @ surgeon_general @ jeromeadamsmd @ cdcgov if we let high # covid19 rates persist which then make social activity and school difficult , we risk incurring a social recession marked by deepening loneliness w/ health consequences just as serious as the economic headwinds we ’ re facing . but it doesn ’ t have to be this way . ( 3/x ) @ margbrennan @ facethenation @ joebiden the data should also be made available to the public so non-governmental scientists can make independent assessments . if the federal government issues an authorization for a vaccine without the support of the scientific community , it would be a mistake . ( end ) @ facethenation @ margbrennan @ joebiden @ surgeon_general @ jeromeadamsmd @ cdcgov i wrote `` together '' on the power of social connection b/c i realized while serving as surgeon general that our relationships w/ one another are one of our greatest sources of healing . this is our time to recommit to building a people centered life and a people centered world . ( end ) @ patgermelman @ joebiden how adorable ! good to know the next generation of scientists has arrived . @ margbrennan @ facethenation @ joebiden whether or not these standards have been met should be publicly affirmed by the career scientists at the food and drug administration ( fda ) and by the vaccine and related biological products advisory committee ( vrbpac ) in a public hearing . ( 2/x ) @ facethenation @ margbrennan @ joebiden @ surgeon_general @ jeromeadamsmd @ cdcgov 2 ) eliminate distractions when you ’ re talking to friends and family ( e.g . checking your inbox or social media ) . 5 minutes of quality time with your full attention is often more fulfilling than 60 minutes of distracted conversation . ( 6/x ) @ margbrennan @ facethenation @ joebiden in order for a vaccine to receive an emergency use authorization from the government , it should meet high standards for safety and efficacy . no corners should be cut in this process . science not politics should guide this critical decision . ( 1/x ) @ facethenation @ margbrennan @ joebiden @ surgeon_general @ jeromeadamsmd @ cdcgov 3 ) find ways to serve others . calling to check on a friend , delivering food to a neighbor , virtually babysitting for a friend for 10-15 minutes so they have a moment to breathe . service is one of our most powerful antidotes to loneliness . ( 7/x ) @ facethenation @ margbrennan @ joebiden and he will need to build strong partnerships from day one with states , faith and community organizations , health care facilities , educational institutions , and employers . all these groups will be essential to a strong , effective # covid19 response . ( end )
