. @ joebiden will be the most pro-equality president we have ever had . i ’ m so proud and so grateful to have such a strong champion for the rights of lgbtq people as the democratic nominee . https : //t.co/mqwc352ohg @ adamnagourney @ thomaskaplan five years ago today , w/ a landmark supreme court ruling making # marriageequality the law of the land nationwide , america took a giant step forward down the path toward full equality . electing @ joebiden this november will put us back on that path and move us even closer . ( thread ) rt @ joebiden : four years ago today , 49 lives were cut short in an act of unspeakable terrorism at pulse nightclub . as we remember those we it is impossible to overstate what this decision means for lgbtq people across this country , whose state and federal governments have failed to protect against employment discrimination . next congress must pass the # equalityact so @ joebiden can sign it into law . https : //t.co/u3tarpykns . @ joebiden is n't even president yet and he 's participating in briefings far longer & amp ; more intensive than trump could ever dream of sitting through . we need a president who makes decisions based on facts and intel - not irrational impulses . https : //t.co/jybzby33jk rt @ joebiden : donald trump has turned our country into a battlefield riven by old resentments and fresh fears . he thinks division helps him at @ hrc ’ s columbus gala last night , @ joebiden declared the # equalityact his top legislative priority . we ’ re grateful for his years of leadership on lgbtq equality . https : //t.co/cjkr44ajyh i was proud to vote early for @ joebiden today in the california primary ! https : //t.co/jgbaeevfuq as vice president , & amp ; now , with the @ bidenfoundation ’ s focus on lgbtq rights at home & amp ; abroad , @ joebiden has worked for & amp ; with the lgbtq community for decades . honored to welcome him to @ hrc 's columbus dinner ! https : //t.co/adptpatxkw looking forward to welcoming a steadfa